	<div style="padding: 4px;"><span class="postbody"><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="2" border="0" align="center" class="quote"><tr>	<td class="quote">still haven't figured out wha the "limited number of heals"</td>	</tr></table>
<br />

<br />
As I see it (just got this spell last night, woohoo!)  The entire group receives the healing spell, however, if the nuke happy wizard is taking all the hits, he uses up the groups sermon, it will only heal for so many heals per group, (whomever is taking damage) per person.  I liked using this prior to a pull when it looked like there were one too many mobs.</span></div>
